videos.description: Ryan McMahon quickly releases the 3-pointer from deep and gets nothing but net.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (McMahon drains the triple from deep) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: McMahon drains the triple from deep

videos.description: It doesn't take long for the Orange to respond as Buddy Boeheim knocks down the triple.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Boeheim responds back with a 3) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boeheim responds back with a 3

videos.description: Elijah Hughes sees the bounce pass to Steven Enoch and denies his layup at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Hughes gets the block from behind) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hughes gets the block from behind

videos.description: Great Louisville ball movement gives Jordan Nwora time to knock down the 3-pointer and the fans love it.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Nwora lights the crowd up with a corner 3) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nwora lights the crowd up with a corner 3

videos.description: Louisville's Ryan McMahon drains another triple sending fans to their feet, but Buddy Boeheim quickly responds and a hush blows over the area.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Boeheim silences Cardinals' fans with a rebuttal 3) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boeheim silences Cardinals' fans with a rebuttal 3

videos.description: David Johnson grabs the offensive rebound which leads to great ball movement, and Jordan Nwora caps it off with a layup and a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Johnson's hustle gives Louisville multiple chances to score) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson's hustle gives Louisville multiple chances to score

videos.description: Every Cardinal on the court gets their hands on the ball before leading it down to Steven Enoch who caps it all off with a two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Louisville's ball handling leads to a Enoch slam) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Louisville's ball handling leads to a Enoch slam

videos.description: Syracuse head coach Jim Boeheim expresses his thoughts on one of his players not getting a foul, and the refs reward him with a technical.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (An angry coach Boeheim gets a technical) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: An angry coach Boeheim gets a technical

videos.description: Jordan Nwora scores 19 points and Ryan McMahon tacks on 13 as both players come up clutch for Louisville in their 90-66 win over Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Nwora, McMahon fuel Cardinals’ rout of Orange) 2020/02/19 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Nwora, McMahon fuel Cardinals' rout of Orange
